:::Atma/Psuedo/Time Warp/Wheeljack:::

::Psuedo kisses her::
Psuedo: I doubt you'll screw it up, but if thats what you want, then we will 
help in the fight.
::They run into the base.  Atma turns to Perplex::
Atma: Hi, im Atma and this is Psuedo.  Were with Technosis and she said that 
theres someone attacking you.  We want to help, so could you clue us in?
~~~~~
::Time Warp reaches the CF, and sees that the brotherhood is attacking.  
Although worried about getting involved in a battle, he runs up to Iron 
Raptor::
Time Warp: You seem occupied, but could you help me?  My brother Airbomber 
and i are looking for a bot named Infectra, is she here?
~~~~~
Wheeljack: No, i dont beleive it does(tell me if im wrong), but its a great 
idea.  If any aquatic bots attack us, they would get pulverized as badly as 
aerial and ground bots.

--part1_fb.11a799b1.27bc8f04_boundary
